TRAP DETECTION: Spotting mundane traps before they trigger

Category: Rogue
Base skill: 35% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Noticing tripwires, pressure plates, and other mechanical traps set
by people, not magic or military ordnance, before they go off. A
rogue's situational awareness skill, distinct from the more technical
Trap and Mine Detection used by soldiers and demolitions experts.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, trap and mine detection, detect ambush
